features: ☕MODERN AND ELEGANT DESIGN TO ENRICH YOUR SPACE: With the combination of pure white panels and vintage wood grain, our kitchen storage cabinet adds a touch of sophistication to any room. Here are two different top panel colors for your choice: retro wood grain and grey wood grain.

☕AMPLE STORAGE SPACE FOR ALL YOUR NEEDS: With two drawers and two doors, our storage island provides plenty of room for storing various items such as kitchenware, clothes, books, toiletries, and decorations. The middle shelf can be adjusted up or down by 2.6 inches, or removed to accommodate larger items.

☕VERSATILE STORAGE CABINET FOR VARIOUS SCENES: Our multi-functional storage cabinet is perfect for any room in your home. Use it as a kitchen pantry cabinet, dining room buffet sideboard, living room storage organizer, entryway console table, or office coffee bar. There are many more uses waiting for you to explore!

☕STURDY AND DURABLE FOR LONG-TERM USE: Our cabinet measures 35.4’’ L x 15.7’’ W x 32’’ H and can hold up to 80lbs on the top panel and 45lbs in each drawer (measuring 14.6‘’ x 11.8‘’ x 4.5’'). It is made of high-quality MDF boards for long-lasting durability and sturdiness. The waterproof panels are scratch-resistant and easy to clean.

☕CLEAR INSTRUCTIONS WITH EXCELLENT CUSTOMER SERVICE: Our kitchen buffet cabinet comes with clear and easy-to-follow instructions. Our professional customer service team is available 24/7 to answer any questions or concerns you may have. We are committed to providing the best service to our customers at all times!

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Gizoon Kitchen Storage Buffet Cabinet Say goodbye to clutter and welcome a clean and organized space with our versatile kitchen storage island.

Gizoon Kitchen Buffet Sideboard Looking for a sturdy and spacious storage cabinet to organize your home? Look no further than our high-quality kitchen cabinet. Designed to withstand the rigors of daily use, our cabinet is built to last and offers ample storage space for all your kitchen essentials. With its solid construction and spacious drawers, our cabinet provides a versatile storage solution that can be used in multiple settings, from your kitchen to your dining room, entryway, or office.

Advantages Arc Corner Design The rounded corners ensure that it is a safe addition to your home. No need to worry about accidentally bumping and injuring yourself or your family. Elegant Door Handles The circular door handles add a touch of elegance to your kitchen. The simple and comfortable design makes it easy to grip and pull open the doors. Magnetic Doors The magnetic doors make it open and close a breeze, also reducing the noise made when closing. This is useful if you have little ones sleeping nearby. Chic Leg Design The chic design of the legs leaves 3'' of space underneath the cabinet. This makes cleaning the area much easier and helps to keep your space neat.

Extra storage space with drawers With 2 drawers, this kitchen storage cabinet provides you with extra storage space for your kitchen essentials. Keep your kitchen organized and clutter-free with this versatile storage solution. Adjustable Shelf The adjustable shelves in this cabinet make it a versatile storage solution. With the ability to move the shelves up or down by 2.6'', you can customize the cabinet to meet your specific storage needs.

Used in diverse settings Kitchen Storage Island Keep all your cooking essentials organized in our versatile kitchen storage cabinet. With spacious drawers and adjustable shelves, you can easily store pots, pans, microwaves, bakers, juicers, coffee machines, tableware, and utensils, keeping your kitchen organized. Used in diverse settings Dining Room Buffet Sideboard Our stylish kitchen cabinet can also be used as a dining room buffet cabinet. With its ample storage space, adjustable shelves, and spacious drawers, you can store all your tableware, linens, and serving dishes to provide an elegant dining experience for your friends. Used in diverse settings Entryway Console Cabinet Transform your entryway with our storage cabinet that doubles as an entryway console table. With its compact size and 2 drawers, you can store your daily essentials, like mail, keys, and shoes, keeping your entryway organized and neat. Used in diverse settings Office Coffee Bar Use our versatile kitchen cabinet as a stylish coffee bar in your office space. You can store all your coffee-making essentials, including coffee beans, tea bags, cups, mugs, water dispensers, coffee machines, and supplies. The cabinet can provide a convenient and practical space for coffee breaks.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 12, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars The coffee bar table I was looking for!!!
reviews.reviewText: I love how slim it is, our kitchen is fairly small so I wanted something that would fit snugly next to my fridge and without getting in the way of the door entrance and this was perfect! Assembly took about 3 hours by myself.Price is very reasonable, and I like that I can remove the middle shelf inside the cabinets for more height, which now stores a lot of my tools for when I cook and don’t have to have it all out in display looking cluttered. The wood illusion seems to scratch very easily, edges came faded out a bit but I’m not too picky, overall colors are very pretty and warm.The doors for the cabinets may have been user error on my part as they are not aligned but no biggie. Overall 10/10:), aesthetically pleasing , great storage, easy to follow instructions!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Easy to assemble
reviews.reviewText: This product was by far the easiest thing I’ve had to assemble from Amazon. It’s pretty sturdy. The instructions were clear. It’s not as tall as I thought it would be but it’s wider than I thought as well. It’s a very beautiful cabinet.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 12, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Good product, but top is dinged up in a few spots
reviews.reviewText: I love this cabinet. I ordered it to go in my kitchen. It came before the arrival date. It took me 2 hours to put together but that’s just me as I like to put it together correctly. The cabinet itself is great, except the brown top was scratched on the under side and it looks like someone put brown stain over it to cover it up. The very top of the brown top is dinged in a few spots, maybe due to careless people. Overall, it’s a good cabinet, just will have to live with the dings. Pretty easy to put together as the instructions were good.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 12, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very pretty and sturdy.
reviews.reviewText: It took a good three hours to put together. Wasn't too difficult. Very pretty in my kitchen.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 14, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Beautiful… I bought 2!
reviews.reviewText: I bought one of these for my kitchen being my kitchen is so small and I don't have a pantry. I love the look and feel of it. It took 2 hours to put one together (by myself) but directions were easy to follow so just take your time. I was worried about it being junk but the only flimsy parts were the back and the bottom of the drawers. The back came with plastic wedges that screwed in to tighten the back so that helped (I wish the drawers had them too). I considered looking for some next time I’m at a hardware store and maybe caulking the bottoms just for added support. 🤷🏻‍♀️ I loved this piece so much I bought a second one for my small dining area too! I highly recommend!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 23, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I love it ! Was hard to put together but it’s so nice.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 18, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars It’s great for the price.
reviews.reviewText: The only thing I am not happy with it the magnet fit the cabinet doors is not strong enough. Doesn’t hold onto the doors at all. Also, the edges of the counter pieces are all chipped. I may have just got a bad batch but for the price, it’s good. I like it for now it’s cute but I don’t see it lasting for years.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 9, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Low quality of construction. Joints are not smoothly connected. The paint job is poor quality.
